      "start": 38.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 47.86000061035156,
      "text": "I can stand up and dance to this groove Open the tab and dunk down their booze",
      "start": 42.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 52.68000030517578,
      "text": "Another person plays on, thanks to our views Camotrain Muse blew up by the news",
      "start": 47.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 57.400001525878906,
      "text": "There's more to display, I need to choose Today is the day, I stop for real clues",
      "start": 52.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 59.7599983215332,
      "text": "My first impressions, I don't care who you are",
      "start": 57.400001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 61.459999084472656,
      "text": "Gon' let loose, let loose",
      "start": 59.7599983215332
    },
    {
